 Krampfhaftigkeit und Ängstlichkeit der meisten westlichen Nationen im Umgang mit Migration widerspiegelt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aRefugeeszGermanyzBrandenburg (State). 4aBrandenburg. 4aDeutschland. 4aDiskriminierung. 4aFlucht. 4aFlüchtlingsforschung. 4aIdentität. 4aIntegration. 4aMigrationspolitik. 4aSolidarität. 4aSozialarbeit. 4aSozialpolitik. 4aSoziologie. 4aVielfalt. 4aZugehörigkeit. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Emigration & Immigration.2bisacsh  aBelonging.  aBrandenburg.  aDiscrimination.  aDiversity.  aFleeing.  aGermany.  aIdentity.  aIntegration.  aMigration Policy.  aRefugee Studies.  aSocial Policy.  aSocial Work.  aSociology.  aSolidarity.1 aKeeling, Laila, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLejaille, Nadia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSalehi, Sahba, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aZyla, Anjali, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2023z9783111024950oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839469866?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839469866423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839469866/original  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-TGPb2023